@startuml
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

skinparam actor {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #E2EFDA
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam boundary {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #B4C7E7
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam control {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #FFD966
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam entity {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #F4B084
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam note {
  BorderColor gray
  BackgroundColor #FFFFA0
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam ranksep 80
skinparam nodesep 70

actor 管理员 as Admin

boundary "订单列表页面" as OrderListPage
boundary "订单详情页面" as OrderDetailPage

control "管理员订单控制器" as AdminOrderController
control "订单服务" as OrderService
control "商品服务" as ProductService

entity "订单" as Order
entity "订单项" as OrderItem
entity "商品" as Product

Admin -down-> OrderListPage : 查看订单列表
Admin -right-> OrderDetailPage : 查看订单详情

OrderListPage -down-> AdminOrderController : 获取订单列表
OrderDetailPage -down-> AdminOrderController : 发货/取消订单

AdminOrderController -down-> OrderService : 调用
OrderService -right-> ProductService : 取消订单时调用
OrderService -down-> Order : 操作
OrderService -right-> OrderItem : 引用
ProductService -down-> Product : 更新库存

note bottom of OrderListPage : 显示所有订单\n按状态筛选
note bottom of OrderDetailPage : 订单详情展示\n操作按钮
note right of AdminOrderController : 处理管理员订单请求
note right of OrderService : 订单状态管理\n订单统计
note right of ProductService : 取消订单时\n恢复商品库存
@enduml